  "notes": "Reconstructed Late Proto-Slavic (c. 600вҖ“800 CE). Key features: open syllable law (no closed syllables), palatalisation alternations (three Slavic palatalisations), nasal vowels /бәҪ Гө/, yers /Дӯ Еӯ/, yat /ГҰЛҗ/. Transcription follows standard Slavicist convention.",
